data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home conveniently located near downtown restaurants, library and pool! Two inviting spaces include a cozy sunroom and living room with a beautiful gas fireplace. Tons of storage with a main floor bedroom. All appliances stay. Furnace NEW 2023 (10 yr. warranty), Dishwasher 2022 and Sump pump 2023, Sunroom New carpet 12/23. Detached garage offers a separate workshop area. Back yard stone patio is great for entertaining or just read a book. Electric average $120, Ohio Gas $75, Sewer and water $ 63. Set you appointment today!
